      "message": "I know this is a bit picky, but I generally think of \"dispatch\" to indicate the handling of something within the current process, whereas in this case, it's really meaning to send or transmit something to another system.  Should it perhaps be renamed (and the comments changed)?\n\nThis comment would also apply to the class name and any variables named \"dispatcher\"",
